{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1266,"text":"In 2002, a group of treatment activists met"},{"time":5755,"text":"to discuss the early development of the airplane."},{"time":9785,"text":"The Wright Brothers, in the beginning of the last century,"},{"time":14486,"text":"had for the first time managed"},{"time":16188,"text":"to make one of those devices fly."},{"time":18760,"text":"They also had taken out numerous patents"},{"time":22023,"text":"on essential parts of the airplane."},{"time":23999,"text":"They were not the only ones."},{"time":25440,"text":"That was common practice in the industry,"},{"time":29024,"text":"and those who held patents on airplanes"},{"time":31316,"text":"were defending them fiercely"},{"time":32472,"text":"and suing competitors left and right."}]},{"cues":[{"time":35894,"text":"This actually wasn't so great for the development of the aviation industry,"},{"time":40811,"text":"and this was at a time that in particular the U.S. government"},{"time":44117,"text":"was interested in ramping up"},{"time":46674,"text":"the production of military airplanes."},{"time":49363,"text":"So there was a bit of a conflict there."},{"time":52074,"text":"The U.S. government decided to take action,"},{"time":55313,"text":"and forced those patent holders"},{"time":57645,"text":"to make their patents available to share with others"},{"time":61806,"text":"to enable the production of airplanes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":67315,"text":"So what has this"},{"time":70285,"text":"got to do with this?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":74305,"text":"In 2002, Nelson Otwoma, a Kenyan social scientist,"},{"time":79368,"text":"discovered he had HIV and needed access to treatment."},{"time":84509,"text":"He was told that a cure did not exist."},{"time":88744,"text":"AIDS, he heard, was lethal,"},{"time":91947,"text":"and treatment was not offered. This was at a time"},{"time":95140,"text":"that treatment actually existed in rich countries."},{"time":97908,"text":"AIDS had become a chronic disease."},{"time":100903,"text":"People in our countries here in Europe, in North America,"},{"time":104504,"text":"were living with HIV, healthy lives."},{"time":107449,"text":"Not so for Nelson. He wasn't rich enough,"},{"time":110284,"text":"and not so for his three-year-old son, who he discovered a year later"},{"time":114256,"text":"also had HIV."}]},{"cues":[{"time":117496,"text":"Nelson decided to become a treatment activist"},{"time":120916,"text":"and join up with other groups."},{"time":123045,"text":"In 2002, they were facing a different battle."},{"time":129388,"text":"Prices for ARVs, the drugs needed to treat HIV,"},{"time":134103,"text":"cost about 12,000 [dollars] per patient per year."},{"time":138500,"text":"The patents on those drugs were held"},{"time":141025,"text":"by a number of Western pharmaceutical companies"},{"time":146796,"text":"that were not necessarily willing"},{"time":149717,"text":"to make those patents available."},{"time":152958,"text":"When you have a patent, you can exclude"},{"time":155130,"text":"anyone else from making, from producing or making"},{"time":159859,"text":"low-cost versions, for example,"},{"time":162857,"text":"available of those medications."},{"time":166433,"text":"Clearly this led to patent wars breaking out"},{"time":170694,"text":"all over the globe."}]},{"cues":[{"time":173652,"text":"Luckily, those patents did not exist everywhere."},{"time":177313,"text":"There were countries that did not recognize"},{"time":179705,"text":"pharmaceutical product patents, such as India,"},{"time":182624,"text":"and Indian pharmaceutical companies"},{"time":185145,"text":"started to produce so-called generic versions,"},{"time":189104,"text":"low-cost copies of antiretroviral medicines,"},{"time":193571,"text":"and make them available in the developing world,"},{"time":196868,"text":"and within a year the price had come down"},{"time":199584,"text":"from 10,000 dollars per patient per year"},{"time":203370,"text":"to 350 dollars per patient per year,"},{"time":205872,"text":"and today that same triple pill cocktail"},{"time":209388,"text":"is available for 60 dollars per patient per year,"},{"time":212224,"text":"and of course that started to have an enormous effect"},{"time":215588,"text":"on the number of people who could afford access"},{"time":218677,"text":"to those medicines."},{"time":220167,"text":"Treatment programs became possible,"},{"time":222745,"text":"funding became available, and the number of people"},{"time":225859,"text":"on antiretroviral drugs started to increase very rapidly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":232620,"text":"Today, eight million people"},{"time":235333,"text":"have access to antiretroviral drugs."},{"time":238449,"text":"Thirty-four million are infected with HIV."},{"time":242431,"text":"Never has this number been so high,"},{"time":244430,"text":"but actually this is good news,"},{"time":245672,"text":"because what it means is people stop dying."},{"time":248305,"text":"People who have access to these drugs stop dying."},{"time":250625,"text":"And there's something else."},{"time":251961,"text":"They also stop passing on the virus."},{"time":254745,"text":"This is fairly recent science that has shown that."},{"time":258407,"text":"What that means is we have the tools"},{"time":261063,"text":"to break the back of this epidemic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":264820,"text":"So what's the problem?"},{"time":270089,"text":"Well, things have changed."},{"time":271955,"text":"First of all, the rules have changed."},{"time":275783,"text":"Today, all countries are obliged to provide"},{"time":281714,"text":"patents for pharmaceuticals that last at least 20 years."},{"time":286236,"text":"This is as a result of the intellectual property rules"},{"time":289172,"text":"of the World Trade Organization."},{"time":291520,"text":"So what India did is no longer possible."},{"time":294699,"text":"Second, the practice of patent-holding companies have changed."},{"time":300036,"text":"Here you see the patent practices"},{"time":304420,"text":"before the World Trade Organization's rules, before '95,"},{"time":308509,"text":"before antiretroviral drugs."},{"time":310894,"text":"This is what you see today,"},{"time":313594,"text":"and this is in developing countries, so what that means is,"},{"time":316282,"text":"unless we do something deliberate"},{"time":318705,"text":"and unless we do something now,"},{"time":321088,"text":"we will very soon be faced with another drug price crisis,"},{"time":326204,"text":"because new drugs are developed,"},{"time":328424,"text":"new drugs go to market, but these medicines are patented"},{"time":331786,"text":"in a much wider range of countries."},{"time":334855,"text":"So unless we act, unless we do something today,"},{"time":339492,"text":"we will soon be faced [with] what some have termed"},{"time":343424,"text":"the treatment time bomb."}]},{"cues":[{"time":346468,"text":"It isn't only the number of drugs that are patented."},{"time":351327,"text":"There's something else that can really scare"},{"time":354110,"text":"generic manufacturers away."},{"time":355951,"text":"This shows you a patent landscape."},{"time":359952,"text":"This is the landscape of one medicine."},{"time":363636,"text":"So you can imagine that if you are a generic company"},{"time":366237,"text":"about to decide whether to invest"},{"time":368230,"text":"in the development of this product, unless you know"},{"time":371366,"text":"that the licenses to these patents"},{"time":373869,"text":"are actually going to be available,"},{"time":376367,"text":"you will probably choose to do something else."},{"time":379419,"text":"Again, deliberate action is needed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":383352,"text":"So surely"},{"time":385749,"text":"if a patent pool could be established"},{"time":389676,"text":"to ramp up the production of military airplanes,"},{"time":393737,"text":"we should be able to do something similar"},{"time":397271,"text":"to tackle the HIV/AIDS epidemic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":400978,"text":"And we did."},{"time":403041,"text":"In 2010, UNITAID established the Medicines Patent Pool"},{"time":408430,"text":"for HIV."},{"time":411913,"text":"And this is how it works:"},{"time":413542,"text":"Patent holders, inventors"},{"time":417213,"text":"that develop new medicines"},{"time":421058,"text":"patent those inventions,"},{"time":423624,"text":"but make those patents available"},{"time":425375,"text":"to the Medicines Patent Pool. The Medicines Patent Pool"},{"time":428348,"text":"then license those out to whoever needs access to those patents."},{"time":432163,"text":"That can be generic manufacturers."},{"time":433839,"text":"It can also be not-for-profit drug development agencies,"},{"time":437652,"text":"for example."},{"time":439129,"text":"Those manufacturers can then sell those medicines"},{"time":441643,"text":"at much lower cost to people who need access to them,"},{"time":446692,"text":"to treatment programs that need access to them."},{"time":449264,"text":"They pay royalties over the sales to the patent holders,"},{"time":453440,"text":"so they are remunerated for sharing their intellectual property."}]},{"cues":[{"time":463769,"text":"There is one key difference"},{"time":467827,"text":"with the airplane patent pool."},{"time":471187,"text":"The Medicines Patent Pool is a voluntary mechanism."},{"time":476104,"text":"The airplane patent holders were not left a choice"},{"time":479536,"text":"whether they'd license their patents or not."},{"time":481176,"text":"They were forced to do so."},{"time":483380,"text":"That is something that the Medicines Patent Pool cannot do."},{"time":487302,"text":"It relies on the willingness of pharmaceutical companies"},{"time":490654,"text":"to license their patents and make them available"},{"time":494224,"text":"for others to use."}]},{"cues":[{"time":498764,"text":"Today, Nelson Otwoma is healthy."},{"time":503929,"text":"He has access to antiretroviral drugs."},{"time":507911,"text":"His son will soon be 14 years old."},{"time":511688,"text":"Nelson is a member of the expert advisory group"},{"time":514258,"text":"of the Medicines Patent Pool,"},{"time":516717,"text":"and he told me not so long ago,"},{"time":518818,"text":"\"Ellen, we rely in Kenya and in many other countries"},{"time":524359,"text":"on the Medicines Patent Pool to make sure"},{"time":527758,"text":"that new medicines also become available to us,"},{"time":533270,"text":"that new medicines, without delay, become available to us.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":538659,"text":"And this is no longer fantasy."},{"time":542018,"text":"Already, I'll give you an example."},{"time":546497,"text":"In August of this year, the United States drug agency"},{"time":549955,"text":"approved a new four-in-one AIDS medication."},{"time":553904,"text":"The company, Gilead, that holds the patents,"},{"time":556609,"text":"has licensed the intellectual property to the Medicines Patent Pool."},{"time":560845,"text":"The pool is already working today, two months later,"},{"time":564772,"text":"with generic manufacturers to make sure that this product"},{"time":567877,"text":"can go to market at low cost"},{"time":571026,"text":"where and when it is needed. This is unprecedented."},{"time":574436,"text":"This has never been done before."},{"time":576376,"text":"The rule is about a 10-year delay for a new product"},{"time":580095,"text":"to go to market in developing countries, if at all."},{"time":583066,"text":"This has never been seen before."},{"time":587099,"text":"Nelson's expectations are very high,"},{"time":590603,"text":"and quite rightly so. He and his son will need access"},{"time":594872,"text":"to the next generation of antiretrovirals"},{"time":597961,"text":"and the next, throughout their lifetime,"},{"time":601068,"text":"so that he and many others in Kenya and other countries"},{"time":605746,"text":"can continue to live healthy, active lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":610178,"text":"Now we count on the willingness of drug companies"},{"time":613398,"text":"to make that happen. We count on those companies"},{"time":616020,"text":"that understand that it is in the interest, not only in the interest"},{"time":619440,"text":"of the global good, but also in their own interest,"},{"time":622624,"text":"to move from conflict to collaboration,"},{"time":628338,"text":"and through the Medicines Patent Pool they can make that happen."},{"time":631219,"text":"They can also choose not to do that,"},{"time":634615,"text":"but those that go down that road may end up"},{"time":640826,"text":"in a similar situation the Wright brothers ended up with"},{"time":643750,"text":"early last century, facing forcible measures"},{"time":647584,"text":"by government. So they'd better jump now."},{"time":652766,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"}]}]}